  "description": "<p><strong>据外媒报道，Facebook将于本周一(7月8日)开始，向美国用户推出其新款Graph Search(社交图谱搜索)工具。</strong>该功能从1月起开始的测试，允许用户对存储于Facebook的元数据进行高级搜索——诸如\"哪些好友喜欢披头士\"、或者\"好友们最喜欢的东京餐馆\"。Graph Search将于接下去的几周内，面向美国和其它使用美式英语的Facebook用户开放，面向其它语种的开放时间尚不得而知。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e5660fc/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243826.htm&amp;t=Facebook%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%9B%BE%E8%B0%B1%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243826.htm&amp;t=Facebook%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%9B%BE%E8%B0%B1%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243826.htm&amp;t=Facebook%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%9B%BE%E8%B0%B1%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243826.htm&amp;t=Facebook%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%9B%BE%E8%B0%B1%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsporta